      "content": "I'll get you the telemetry logs shortly. In the meantime, just run a preliminary analysis based on the architecture specs you have for this facility. I'm specifically concerned about the high-compute nodes—the ones running the heavy inference models—because they're eating up almost 40% of the total power. If those are the biggest offenders, just list them as candidates for shut down in your report. Don't overcomplicate it, just give me the raw list of what needs to go to hit that 15% mark.",
